description.narrative: Despite that the Sudanese government committed at the highest level ;to making available statistically sound and internationally comparable data on children and women, the covid pandemic and political instability caused delays in implementation of MICS. The Real Time Monitoring (RTM) System ;and vulnerability mapping began rolling out to enhance situation and performance monitoring, inform UNICEF programming, and target the most vulnerable children in Sudan. Although the State of Sudanese Children analysis was not widely disseminated; it was used for consultations and prioritization internally and with partners. | Status:Partially met | As-of Date:18/01/2022
